      <title>塞尔维亚维持利率不变以应对价格压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/serbia-maintains-hold-on-rates-as-it-weighs-price-pressures</link>
      <description><![CDATA[塞尔维亚央行维持借贷成本不变，这一意外举措表明政策制定者在权衡持续的价格压力时采取了谨慎态度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/serbia-maintains-hold-on-rates-as-it-weighs-price-pressures</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 11:00:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
